---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/s3_vectors.rs
expression: formatted
---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search().message.body, vector_search().attempt_count, vector_search().message.status, vector_search().package_weight_kg, round(vector_search().score,Int64(1))                                                                                                 |
|               |   Sort: vector_search().package_weight_kg DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search().score DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |     Projection: vector_search().message.body, vector_search().attempt_count, vector_search().message.status, vector_search().package_weight_kg, round(vector_search().score, Int64(1)), vector_search().score                                                                     |
|               |       BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |         TableScan: vector_search() projection=[message.body, message.status, attempt_count, package_weight_kg, score], full_filters=[vector_search().attempt_count > Int64(1), vector_search().package_weight_kg > Float64(5), vector_search().message.status = Utf8("FAILED")]   |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[message.body@0 as message.body, attempt_count@1 as attempt_count, message.status@2 as message.status, package_weight_kg@3 as package_weight_kg, round(vector_search().score,Int64(1))@4 as round(vector_search().score,Int64(1))]                           |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [package_weight_kg@3 DESC, score@5 DESC], fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[package_weight_kg@3 DESC, score@5 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[message.body@0 as message.body, attempt_count@2 as attempt_count, message.status@1 as message.status, package_weight_kg@3 as package_weight_kg, round(score@4, 1) as round(vector_search().score,Int64(1)), score@4 as score]                         |
|               |         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |           ProjectionExec: expr=[message.body@4 as message.body, message.status@1 as message.status, attempt_count@3 as attempt_count, package_weight_kg@2 as package_weight_kg, score@0 as score]                                                                                 |
|               |             CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |               CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                 HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Left, on=[(event.id@0, event.id@0)], filter=attempt_count@2 > 1 AND package_weight_kg@1 > 5 AND message.status@0 = FAILED, projection=[score@1, message.status@2, package_weight_kg@3, attempt_count@4, message.body@6] |
|               |                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([event.id@0], 3), input_partitions=3                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                       CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                         ProjectionExec: expr=[key@3 as event.id, 1 - distance@4 as score, message.status@0 as message.status, package_weight_kg@1 as package_weight_kg, attempt_count@2 as attempt_count]                                                                         |
|               |                           RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                             BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                               S3VectorsQueryExec: filter={$and:[{attempt_count:{$gt:1}},{package_weight_kg:{$gt:5.0}},{message.status:{$eq:"FAILED"}}]} limit=100                                                                                                                 |
|               |                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([event.id@0], 3), input_partitions=3                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |                           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                             SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                               DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[10]                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
